metadata.name: Tensión entre lo esperable y lo esperado
metadata.description:
Decimos luna llena y nadie se imagina lo que hay detrás de éstas palabras.
Un cuerpo que lee, es un cuerpo que también habla, a veces lee confianza, otras veces, desconfianza, el cuerpo que habla pregunta: quién es.

A tension between what can and what is to be expected. 

We call it  a Full Moon, but no one actually knows what lies behind those words. 
A body who reads that is also a body who talks. Sometimes he reads trust, but other times, he reads mistrust. This body who talks, often wonders: who are you?

Collaborative Process:
-Poetry and collage by Estrujamentes.
-3D art and animation by Buda Studio.
